<h1>Zeus</h1>
<h5>Measuring team workload in a friendly way!</h5>
<h6 class="small-txt">Brainchild of: Josh Guthrie</h6>

<hr>

<p>In Greek mythology, Zeus was the god of the sky, the god of order, and the god of justice. With Zeus, you can easily set your own bandwidth, see who is available to assist on other projects or who is overloaded and needs help.</p>

